    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Summary of Adam Smith&amp;rsquo;s &amp;ldquo;The Wealth of Nations&amp;rdquo; 
    &lt;div id=&#34;summary-of-adam-smiths-the-wealth-of-nations&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
